extends ../template.pug
append variables
  - pageTitle       = 'Privacy'
  - metaDescription = 'This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that Hubb collected.'
  - ogUrl           = 'https://hubb-me.com/privacy.html'
  - ogImage         = 'https://hubb-me.com/assets/images/hubb.jpg'

block body
  //- Privacy Section
  section.legal
    .legal__container.l-container
      h1(class="legal__title legal__title--privacy", data-privacy="Privacy Policy") Privacy Policy

      .legal__description
        p.legal__text At Hubb, accessible from #[a(class="legal__link", href="/") www.hubb-me.com], one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by hubb-me.com and how we use it.
        p.legal__text If you have additional questions or require more information about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us.
        p.legal__text This Privacy Policy applies only to our online activities and is valid for visitors to our website with regards to the information that they shared and/or collect in hubb-me.com. This policy is not applicable to any information collected offline or via channels other than this website.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--odd Consent
        p.legal__text By using our website, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--even Information we collect
        p.legal__text The personal information that you are asked to provide, and the reasons why you are asked to provide it, will be made clear to you at the point we ask you to provide your personal information.
        p.legal__text If you contact us directly, we may receive additional information about you such as your name, email address, phone number, the contents of the message and/or attachments you may send us, and any other information you may choose to provide.
        p.legal__text When you register for an Account, we may ask for your contact information, including items such as name, company name, address, email address, and telephone number.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--odd How we use your information
        p.legal__text We use the information we collect in various ways, including to:

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--even Log Files
        p.legal__text #[a(class="legal__link", href="/") hubb-me.com] follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files log visitors when they visit websites. All hosting companies do this and a part of hosting services' analytics. The information collected by log files include internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date and time stamp, referring/exit pages, and possibly the number of clicks. These are not linked to any information that is personally identifiable. The purpose of the information is for analyzing trends, administering the site, tracking users' movement on the website, and gathering demographic information.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--odd Cookies and Web Beacons
        p.legal__text Like any other website, #[a(class="legal__link", href="/") hubb-me.com] uses 'cookies'. These cookies are used to store information including visitors' preferences, and the pages on the website that the visitor accessed or visited. The information is used to optimize the users' experience by customizing our web page content based on visitors' browser type and/or other information.
        p.legal__text For more general information on cookies, please read "What Are Cookies" from Cookie Consent.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--even Advertising Partners Privacy Policies
        p.legal__text You may consult this list to find the Privacy Policy for each of the advertising partners of #[a(class="legal__link", href="/") hubb-me.com]
        p.legal__text Third-party ad servers or ad networks uses technologies like cookies, JavaScript, or Web Beacons that are used in their respective advertisements and links that appear on #[a(class="legal__link", href="/") hubb-me.com], which are sent directly to users' browser. They automatically receive your IP address when this occurs. These technologies are used to measure the effectiveness of their advertising campaigns and/or to personalize the advertising content that you see on websites that you visit.
        p.legal__text Note that #[a(class="legal__link", href="/") hubb-me.com] has no access to or control over these cookies that are used by third-party advertisers.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--odd Third Party Privacy Policies
        p.legal__text Hubb's Privacy Policy does not apply to other advertisers or websites. Thus, we are advising you to consult the respective Privacy Policies of these third-party ad servers for more detailed information. It may include their practices and instructions about how to opt-out of certain options.
        p.legal__text You can choose to disable cookies through your individual browser options. To know more detailed information about cookie management with specific web browsers, it can be found at the browsers' respective websites.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--even CCPA Privacy Rights
        p.legal__text Under the CCPA, among other rights, California consumers have the right to:
        p.legal__text Request that a business that collects a consumer's personal data disclose the categories and specific pieces of personal data that a business has collected about consumers.
        p.legal__text Request that a business delete any personal data about the consumer that a business has collected.
        p.legal__text Request that a business that sells a consumer's personal data, not sell the consumer's personal data.
        p.legal__text If you make a request, we have one month to respond to you. If you would like to exercise any of these rights, please contact us.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--odd GDPR Data Protection Rights
        p.legal__text We would like to make sure you are fully aware of all of your data protection rights. Every user is entitled to the following:
        p.legal__text The right to access – You have the right to request copies of your personal data. We may charge you a small fee for this service.
        p.legal__text The right to rectification – You have the right to request that we correct any information you believe is inaccurate. You also have the right to request that we complete the information you believe is incomplete.
        p.legal__text The right to erasure – You have the right to request that we erase your personal data, under certain conditions.
        p.legal__text The right to restrict processing – You have the right to request that we restrict the processing of your personal data, under certain conditions.
        p.legal__text The right to object to processing – You have the right to object to our processing of your personal data, under certain conditions.
        p.legal__text The right to data portability – You have the right to request that we transfer the data that we have collected to another organization, or directly to you, under certain conditions.
        p.legal__text If you make a request, we have one month to respond to you. If you would like to exercise any of these rights, please contact us.

      .legal__description
        h2.legal__section.legal__section--even Children's Information
        p.legal__text Another part of our priority is adding protection for children while using the internet. We encourage parents and guardians to observe, participate in, and/or monitor and guide their online activity.
        p.legal__text #[a(class="legal__link", href="/") hubb-me.com] does not knowingly collect any Personal Identifiable Information from children under the age of 13. If you think that your child provided this kind of information on our website, we strongly encourage you to contact us immediately and we will do our best efforts to promptly remove such information from our records.

  //- Columns Section
  include ../includes/columns.pug
